<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT59">
<l>aṉpāvā yāramuta māvā yaṭiyēṉuk</l>
<l>kiṉpāvā yellāmum nīyāvāy poṉpāvai</l>
<l>kēḷvā kiḷaroḷiyeṉ kēcavaṉē kēṭiṉṟi</l>
<l>yāḷvāyk kaṭiyēṉṉā ṉāḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who are love! O You who are the rare nectar!</l>
<l>O You who are joy to me, a servant! O You who are everything!</l>
<l>O Husband of the golden Lady!  O my Keśava with resplendent lustre!</l>
<l>I, a servant, am a servant to You who rule [over me] without evil.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
